name: minU08
codeComment: min value of a 8bit unsigned integer

name: maxU08
codeComment: max value of a 8bit unsigned integer

name: minU16
codeComment: min value of a 16bit unsigned integer

name: maxU16
codeComment: max value of a 16bit unsigned integer

name: minS16
codeComment: min value of a 16bit signed integer

name: maxS16
codeComment: max value of a 16bit signed integer

name: needsBurn
codeComment: 1 if needs a flash page burned

name: flashDataLost
codeComment: 1 if unburned flash page was swapped out

name: currFlashTable
codeComment: current flash table loaded into RAM

name: motorDriverFault
codeComment: 1 if motor driver detected overcurrent or over temp condition, 0 otherwise

name: adcStalled
codeComment: 1 if ADC conversions have stopped, 0 otherwise

name: ppsSafetyDelta
codeComment: delta in the redundant PPS sensor comparison

name: tpsSafetyDelta
codeComment: delta in the redundant TPS sensor comparison

name: idleAdder
codeComment: portion of tps target from idle control

name: ppsAdder
codeComment: portion of tps target from pedal position

name: driverFB
codeComment: motor driver current feedback ADC value (raw)

name: enabled
codeComment: set to 1 to enable real-time data broadcasting

name: ppsCalA
codeComment: min/max ADC range calibration for Pedal Position Sensors (PPS)\n min is ADC at 0% throttle\n max is ADC at 100% throttle

name: ppsCalB
codeComment: min/max ADC range calibration for Pedal Position Sensors (PPS)\n min is ADC at 0% throttle\n max is ADC at 100% throttle

name: tpsCalA
codeComment: min/max ADC range calibration for Throttle Position Sensors (TPS)\n min is ADC at 0% throttle\n max is ADC at 100% throttle

name: tpsCalB
codeComment: min/max ADC range calibration for Throttle Position Sensors (TPS)\n min is ADC at 0% throttle\n max is ADC at 100% throttle
